data.name: FindCoursesByCommentOrProtocolActivity_CommentFieldString_Description
data.value: Filters out the results which do not contain the value of this CommentFieldString (case insensitive, regular expressions are handled as normal characters) in the comment field of the Course for the given Patient. When string is null the comment field is completely ignored, but when the string has an empty value ("") it filters out all the non empty field. The ProtocolFieldString and LogicalOperator parameter are also part of the filter process.

data.name: FindCoursesByCommentOrProtocolActivity_LogicalOperator_Description
data.value: Logical operator on how to combine the CommentFieldString and ProtocolFieldString in the search query (only AND and OR). When one of those search strings is null the operator is ignored and the search query is only applied to the non null string.

data.name: FindCoursesByCommentOrProtocolActivity_PatId1_Description
data.value: The patient ID (_patId1) for which to retrieve the Course records

data.name: FindCoursesByCommentOrProtocolActivity_ProtocolFieldString_Description
data.value: Filters out the results which do not contain the value of this ProtocolFieldString (case insensitive, regular expressions are handled as normal characters) in the protocol field of the Course for the given Patient. When string is null the protocol field is completely ignored, but when the string has an empty value it filters out all the non empty values of the protocol field. The CommentFieldString and LogicalOperator parameter are also part of the filter process.

data.name: FindRxSitesByCommentOrPatternActivity_CommentFieldString_Description

data.name: FindRxSitesByCommentOrPatternActivity_LogicalOperator_Description
data.value: Select one of the operators to combine the selection of Comment and Protocol (default is EntityBooleanOp.Or)

data.name: FindRxSitesByCommentOrPatternActivity_PatternFieldString_Description
